'''Neha Marda''' ({{lang-hi|à¤¨à¥à¤¹à¤¾ à¤®à¤°à¥à¤¦à¤¾}}) is an Indian television actress, popularly known as ''Gehna'' for her role in [[Balika Vadhu]] on [[Colors TV]]. She is from a [[Marwaris|Marwari]] Marda ([[Maheshwari]]) family and was born and brought up in [[Kolkatta]], West Bengal.<ref>{{cite news|last=Yadav|first=Kavita|title=Neha's parents on a groom hunt; she wants an arranged match|url=http://www.tellychakkar.com/snippets/nehas-parents-groom-hunt-she-wants-arranged-match}}</ref>
==TV shows==
Marda has worked in TV serials including: Balika Vadhu (2008-present), [[Ek thi Rajkumari]], [[Saath Rahega Always]] (2005-2006), and [[Jo Ishq ki marzi who rab ki marzi]]. In addition, was offered a film role but had to turn it down "as she was not ready to leave her serials as of now" Besides, she is a wonderful dancer as well.<ref>{{cite news|title=A new career for Neha Marda|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2011-02-09/tv/28543408_1_neha-marda-new-career-gehna|newspaper=Times of India}}</ref>
